---
title: Sweet Ginger Steelhead Trout with Buttery Rice & Roasted Broccoli
description: Pork chops are always a weeknight winner. They’re satisfying, speedy, and so versatile, which is why our chefs are always brainstorming new ways to take ’em to the next level. The kicker this week: a fresh ginger and apricot jam pan sauce. On the side, there’s roasted broccoli and a bed of buttery jasmine rice (perfect for catching any runoff sauce). Prepare for a flavor explosion.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/62324403dfb7cc56295ef85c-72a6e95b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sweet-ginger-steelhead-trout-62324403dfb7cc56295ef85c-1470be24.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/sweet-ginger-steelhead-trout-62324403dfb7cc56295ef85c
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: Asian
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 850 kcal
